data.description: Unlock the potential of this 1584 sq. ft. fixer-upper, a lucrative opportunity for savvy investors. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this property is a canvas awaiting your vision. With some TLC, this home can transform into a profitable asset. Nestled in a promising location, the investment potential is vast, promising both short-term gains and long-term value. Don't miss out on this chance to revitalize and capitalize - a blank slate for your investment success awaits in this 3-bed, 2-bath fixer-upper!
